Each [[Portfolio]] is steered by a [[squad|Autonomous Squad]] made up of its [[Chapter Leader]]s, [[Product Leader]]s and [[Technology Leader]]s. As the peak body of the [[Portfolio]] its primary accountability is to factor and refactor the functional responsibilities of its portfolio's [[squads|Autonomous Squad]] by means of [[Portfolio Mapping]] and to enable the [[Portfolio Leader]] to intelligently liaise with the business's executives to manage the portfolio's finances.
